###
@authToken = {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### Get all leave applications
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leave-management/leave-applications
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get pending leave applications
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leave-management/leave-applications?status=pending
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get approved leave applications
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leave-management/leave-applications?status=approved
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get rejected leave applications
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leave-management/leave-applications?status=rejected
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Update a leave application status (replace with actual leave application ID)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/leave-management/leave-applications/LEAVE_APPLICATION_ID/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "status": "approved",
  "comments": "Leave approved as requested"
}
